.TH vdf_free_node 3

.SH NAME
vdf_free_node

.SH LIBRARY
Valve Data Format Parser Library (libvdfc)

.SH SYNOPSIS
#include <vdfc/vdf.h>

void vdf_free_node(VDFNode *node);

.SH DESCRIPTION
Recursively free a node and all its descendants.
Safe to call with node == NULL (no-op)

.SH PARAMETERS
`VDFNode *node` - The node to free.

.SH RETURN VALUE
None.

.SH ERRORS
None.

